Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘～提問！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒家70符2番是多少點？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.17,0:24:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  4500點！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那莊家的90符2番呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,8700點！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚…完全跟不上啊…

